#: urpm/cli/main.py:353
msgid ""
"Initialize a new urpm setup with standard Mageia media.\n"
"\n"
"Used for creating chroot environments or bootstrapping new systems.\n"
"Mirrors are selected from the Mageia mirror API; the [server] section\n"
"in /etc/urpm/conf.d/10-server.cfg controls geographic filtering\n"
"(country/continent whitelist/blacklist).\n"
"\n"
"Examples:\n"
"  urpm --urpm-root /tmp/rootfs init --release 10\n"
"  urpm --urpm-root /tmp/rootfs init --release cauldron --arch x86_64\n"
"  urpm init --mirrorlist 'https://mirrors.mageia.org/api/"
"mageia.10.x86_64.list'\n"
msgstr ""
"Inicializa uma nova configuração urpm com meios padrão do Mageia.\n"
"\n"
"Utilizado para criar ambientes chroot ou para bootstrap de novos sistemas.\n"
"\n"
"Exemplos:\n"
" urpm --urpm-root /tmp/rootfs init --release 10\n"
" urpm --urpm-root /tmp/rootfs init --release cauldron --arch x86_64\n"
" urpm init --mirrorlist 'https://mirrors.mageia.org/api/"
"mageia.10.x86_64.list'\n"

